The Director of Large-Scale Mining and Mineral Investment Promotion shall, in collaboration with the ministry responsible for finance and the Zambia Development Agency —
(a) develop policies that seek to identify and attract potential investors to the mining industry;
develop policies that seek to identify and attract potential investors to the mining industry;
(b) develop and execute investment promotion awareness programmes and strategies in the mining sector with the aim of enabling the sector to become investment promotion conscious and utilise investment promotion as a tool for innovation and creativity;
